('96064','33139','5','Finca with 3 houses in Mallorca for sale'),
('96065','33140','5','This country house with 3 buildings is situated on a 75,000 m² ca large flat plot, surrounded by a nature conservation zone. The sea is only 15km away.\r\nHouse1 can accommodate 8 Pers. It has about 350m² of living space which are divided into 4 bedrooms (3 twins, 1 double), 3 bathrooms, 1 restroom, living room with fireplace, kitchen, dining area and a billiard room. Outside, there has terraces, a sports area with a basketball, table tennis, pool.\r\nHouse 2 can accommodate 4-6 persons. The Loft-like home has about 60m² of living space with 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms en suite, kitchen, living-dining room, a separate bedroom with bathroom en suite. Again, it has a beautiful terrace to relax and a pool.\r\nHouse 3 currently has a separate entrance and is inhabited by the owner of the finca, but can also be rented. It has approximately 380m² of living space and spread over 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, living-dining room, toilet and kitchen. A landscaped garden and a swimming pool complete the offer. Rental licenses are available. A bright ca 80m² air-conditioned room with parquet floors and large wall mirror can be used as multi-purpose room or Joga room. The property is located in an absolutely quiet location.\r\n'),
